{"id":"tahpenes","term":"Tahpenes","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>The wife of Pharaoh, who gave her sister in marriage to Hadad the Edomite (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 11:19\">1 Kings 11:19</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 11:20\">20</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Kings 11:19","1 Kings 11:20"]}